				<wikidot:authorName>Squamous</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3484071</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The AI analysis wasn't the best part of the article for me, though I do love the explanation surrounding it: the idea of putting an AI in an industrial peeler for more efficient analysis is really funny.<br /> The core concept of this SCP is just so outlandish - boomer comics inside of limes - that I have to upvote it. It's ridiculous. It's hilarious.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
